        <h1>Muffy Montgomery Jones</h1>
        <p class="intro">
          Monty's partner in dynasty management and gala diplomacy ensured the Jones name carried forward the Montgomery legacy
          of polished influence. Though she passed away seven years ago, her meticulous plans still guide every Jones gathering.
        </p>
      </div>
    </header>

