            <p class="card-meta"><span class="meta-label">ID:</span> MFM-01 <span aria-hidden="true">•</span> <span class="meta-label">Date:</span> February 14, 2004</p>
            <p>
              Muffy planned dinner seating like a chessboard, positioning donors opposite policy
              makers to encourage “philanthropic negotiations.” Monty still keeps her annotated charts for reference.
            </p>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="card" id="mfm-memory-02">
