            <p class="card-meta"><span class="meta-label">ID:</span> MFM-02 <span aria-hidden="true">•</span> <span class="meta-label">Date:</span> May 22, 2006</p>
            <p>
              Their prenup included clauses about deductible galas. She maintained a calendar
              tracking which charity got the next spotlight, and Monty keeps it archived as a relic of her precision.
            </p>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="card" id="mfm-memory-03">
          <div class="card-link">
